snippet.title: Pump It Up Infinity | MAWARU INFINITY | S22

• Artist: TaroNuke & Kimsynth
• BPM: ??? (128-222.222)

• Mode & Difficulty | Step Artist:
➤ Single Lv. 22 | TaroNuke

• Additional Notes:
➤ Introduced in the latest and final v1.10 update.
➤ This remix can be unlocked for normal play after passing the "Taronukable!" mission from Mission Zone Infinity.
➤ This is a part of TaroNuke's MAWARU series (mainly for SM/ITG), where players perform various tasks for reward points.
